result.name: Luk Lam Dessert

reviews.text:
This is the famous dessert shop at sham shui pou. Even late night still full with customer.
I have ordered the famous black sesame glutinous rice dumpling. It is so soft and chewy, the sesame is the best I ever tried.
I will return to try others.
Quality has been maintained very well. Surprisingly not crowded.
I’ve visited this Chinese dessert soup more than 20 years. There’s no English menu but you can refer to the picture in menu. They serve traditional Chinese dessert soup which is highly recommended.
The dessert is tasteful and innovative
Very good desert.
